body.description: Product Description Fact: Dull, smudgy ink is a downer. So boost your writing fun factor with Paper Mate Flair Pens. With a rainbow of bright colors and smear resistant ink that won’t bleed through the page, these colored pens make writing a blast. The medium point (0.7 mm) writes in bold, colorful lines so your self-expression makes a major statement. The best part of all? Everything you can create—whether you’re taking notes, bullet journaling, drawing, doodling, or doing anything else that inspires you. With Paper Mate Flair Pens, there’s no limit to your fun. From the Manufacturer The Paper Mate Flair Felt Tip Marker Pen provides bold and expressive lines and is great for editing documents and papers. This writing instrument features a point guard to protect the felt tip, and quick-drying, water-based ink that doesn't bleed through paper.What's in the Box 12-pack of vibrant Paper Mate Flair Felt Marker Pens.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Write beautifully, and don’t bleed!
reviews.reviewText: These pens are some of my favorites, and I use a LOT of pens and markers. These write well, won’t smudge, and don’t bleed through my pages. I’ve been using these to mark up and write in my journaling scriptures, and they work wonders. The variety of colors is great with a mix of pastel, bright, and bold. I would definitely recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Awesome pens, awesome holiday price
reviews.reviewText: I love the quality of Flair pens and when these went to below $6, I bought several as Christmas gifts. Bright luscious colors and smooth tips make it satisfying to write in a journal or do some sketching.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 19, 2023
reviews.reviewText: My friends all had these pens and I decided to buy them, too, and here are my results:1. They arrived earlier than expected2. They work well and the color is really cute3. reviews.reviewText: I work in an office, so I write all throughout the day, and these are my favorite pens ever. They are very pretty colors, they write smoothly, and they do not smear

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect Writing Companion
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the Paper Mate Felt Tip Pens, and I must say, they have exceeded my expectations! The pens glide effortlessly across the paper, providing a smooth and consistent writing experience. The ink is vibrant and dries quickly, eliminating any worries about smudging. The pens are also very comfortable to hold, even during long writing sessions, which is a huge plus for me. Moreover, the durability of the tips is impressive; they maintain their shape and don’t fray, ensuring precise lines every time. Whether for note-taking, journaling, or artistic endeavors, these pens have proven to be incredibly versatile. I highly recommend the Paper Mate Felt Tip Pens to anyone in need of reliable, high-quality writing instruments. Five stars for sure!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 5, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I'm so happy I bought this! I got it in a lighting deal and it was such a good value for how many pens you get. I like that it includes both the felt tip and ball point pens. Neither variety bleeds or smudges and both work well and have vibrant color. These will be perfect for my new planner, recipe cards, and my general compulsive list making.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Best markers for notes
reviews.reviewText: As a college student, i like these for indicating different things within my notes. They are vibrant and smooth to use. It makes you want to use them more when they feel good.They don’t feel cheap.They don't bleed through unless you use thin paper like in bluebooks. Work on notebooks which is more important.Vibrance is awesome.Only time will tell if they last however.Will update accordingly once they’re done.Overall, really nice feel, nice color and build is nice.
